{"tid":671890,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"前度同我講既一番說話","createTime":"2018-05-20T13:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T08:12:03.000Z","uid":16740,"like":118,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c64cc6658e00916caa0861f31b9a7e48f5ba35d5","tid":671890,"uid":16740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:34:53.000Z","msg":"講番小小背景先，係幾年前既事。<br />\n<br />\n我同佢識左兩年，之後表白成功，一齊左半個月都無就派左帽俾我，佢話揾到個更好既，所以就做番朋友，果陣都唔開心左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後隔左一年就收到佢既請帖，當然我都無去到，俾左人情就算。之後望到Facebook 知佢生左個仔<br />\n<br />\n早排前度whatsapp番我，講下近況<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =前度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢排點呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係咁，番工番學<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁上進呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早知當初跟你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解咁講？你唔開心？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔係好幸福咩，見你Facebook post哂啲幸福照<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉，我發現老公有第二個，係佢個袋到發現dom，我平時同佢都唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (心入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n如是者，佢好似搞緊離婚了，廿幾歲帶住個1歲既仔。"},{"pid":"364dd092df564b92580cbf60063e1f7109a63990","tid":671890,"uid":41602,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:37:23.000Z","msg":"咁你開香檳慶祝未呀"},{"pid":"088239e3bf5d30a0190acc6ea016405e04adb0c4","tid":671890,"uid":63449,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"有報應！<br />\n抵死！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31ec9ac884c7485de546edd0f7a0a1de118233a","tid":671890,"uid":16740,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"364dd092df564b92580cbf60063e1f7109a63990","tid":671890,"uid":41602,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:37:23.000Z","msg":"咁你開香檳慶祝未呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:55:08.000Z","msg":"開左"},{"pid":"486cbae39085b416d080ef7376ccb6cf6659bb7a","tid":671890,"uid":16740,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"088239e3bf5d30a0190acc6ea016405e04adb0c4","tid":671890,"uid":63449,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"有報應！<br />\n抵死！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:55:19.000Z","msg":"我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b084fc2536ed4105ecff6674a874f1733f618622","tid":671890,"uid":63449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"486cbae39085b416d080ef7376ccb6cf6659bb7a","tid":671890,"uid":16740,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"088239e3bf5d30a0190acc6ea016405e04adb0c4","tid":671890,"uid":63449,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"有報應！<br />\n抵死！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T13:55:19.000Z","msg":"我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyT